These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
There 4 different types of food: pineapple, garlic, eggplant, cucumber
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, tulip, rose, poppy
1. the person eating eggplant is between the person who growsrose and the person who growstulip##2
2. the person eating cucumber is on the left or right of the person who growsrose##3
3. the person who growsrose is not to the left of the person who growsrose##8
4. the person who growstulip is not the person eating eggplant##6
5. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the right of the person eating pineapple##5
6. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | cucumber  | pineapple | eggplant | garlic  |
| Flower   | daisy | rose   | poppy  | tulip |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, soy-milk, milk, water
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, climbing, parkour, cycling
1. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##8
2. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the right of the person drinking water##5
3. the person drinking 7up is the person who's sport is climbing##1
4. the person drinking water is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking soy-milk##2
5. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person who's sport is biathlon##7
6. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is not to the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | milk | soy-milk          | water | 7up     |
| Sport    | parkour      | cycling | biathlon | climbing |

