.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, 7up, fanta, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, ice-hockey, cricket, badminton
1. the person who's sport is swimming is not to the left of the person drinking fanta##8
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking water##1
4. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person drinking water is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Beverage           | water | 7up | fanta     | hot-chocolate |
| Sport   | ice-hockey    | badminton   | swimming | cricket    |

