.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, balloon-flower, amaryllis, dahlia
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, february, december, march
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in february##8
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the person who growsdahlia is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##8
5. the person who growsmarigold is the person who's birthday is in august##1
6. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
7. the person who growsamaryllis is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdahlia##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Flower   | amaryllis   | balloon-flower         | dahlia   | marigold    |
| Birthday         | february | march | december | august |

