.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, kale, artichoke, grapefruit
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: february, october, may, january
1. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere between the person eating lettuce and the person eating kale##7
2. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in may##5
3. the person eating grapefruit is somewhere between the person eating artichoke and the person eating lettuce##7
4. the person eating artichoke is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##8
5. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere between the person eating kale and the person who's birthday is in october##7
6. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapefruit##5
7. the person who's birthday is in october is not to the left of the person eating lettuce##8
8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Food   | kale   | artichoke | grapefruit | lettuce    |
| Birthday         | february | january   | may   | october |

