.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, indonesian, colombian, russian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, musical, fantasy, thriller
1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
2. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the american##5
3. the colombian is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
4. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
5. the american is somewhere to the left of the indonesian##5
6. the russian is not to the left of the person watching musical movies##8
7. the russian is the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality          | russian | american | indonesian  | colombian |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | thriller         | fantasy | drama |

