2. the owner of the horse is somewhere between the russian and the owner of the fish##7
3. the owner of the fish is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
4. the owner of the horse is not to the left of the owner of the cat##8
5. the owner of the horse is not to the left of the malaysian##8
6. the spanish is on the left or right of the american##3
7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
8. the spanish is on the left of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | malaysian      | american | spanish | russian   |
| Pet      | cat | fish | horse  | chinchilla |

