.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-8::.
There 4 different types of food: plum, kiwi, papaya, lettuce
4 different games are played: scrabble, poker, chess, domino
1. the person eating papaya is not to the right of the person playing domino##8
2. the person playing domino is somewhere to the right of the person playing chess##5
3. the person eating kiwi is on the left of the person playing chess##1
4. the person playing chess is somewhere between the person playing poker and the person eating kiwi##7
5. the person eating papaya is not to the right of the person eating lettuce##8
6. the person eating lettuce is somewhere between the person playing poker and the person eating papaya##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |      2       |        3        |     4      |
| Food     | kiwi | papaya | lettuce | plum     |
| Game   | scrabble   | chess        | domino          | poker |

