.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, comedy, crime, satire
4 different games are played: monopoly, snooker, whist, chess
1. the person watching documentary movies is between the person watching satire movies and the person playing monopoly##2
2. the person playing chess is on the far left##1
3. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3
4. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the right of the person playing monopoly##5
5. the person playing snooker is the person playing snooker##1
6. the person watching crime movies is not the person playing whist##6
7. the person watching satire movies is not to the right of the person watching crime movies##8
8. the person playing monopoly is not to the left of the person playing snooker##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | satire   | documentary | crime | comedy |
| Game     | chess | snooker       | monopoly  | whist    |

