.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, hot-chocolate, milk
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, fisherman, dressmaker, lawyer
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is not to the right of the lawyer##8
2. the doctor is not to the right of the person drinking juice##8
3. the fisherman is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
4. the doctor is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the lawyer and the dressmaker##2
6. the person drinking juice is on the far left##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the lawyer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Beverage    | juice        | milk | hot-chocolate      | coffee    |
| Job   | doctor | dressmaker   | fisherman | lawyer |

