.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
City: colone, prague, miami, liverpool
4 different pets are kept: mouse, snake, rabbit, dog
1. the owner of the dog is not to the right of the owner of the mouse##8
2. the owner of the dog is not to the right of the person traveling to colone##8
3. the owner of the snake is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
4. the person traveling to colone is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the mouse is somewhere between the owner of the rabbit and the person traveling to prague##7
7. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
8. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| City   | liverpool | prague         | miami    | colone       |
| Pet      | snake | dog | mouse | rabbit |

