.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-14::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, van, motorbike, subway
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, emerald, blood-red, turquise
1. the person who likes turquise is not to the left of the person who likes emerald##8
2. the person driving the subway is in an odd position##4
3. the person who likes turquise is somewhere to the right of the person driving the subway##5
4. the person driving the van is between the person driving the subway and the person who likes blood-red##2
5. the person driving the roller is on the far left##1
6. the person who likes red is between the person who likes emerald and the person who likes turquise##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| Transport   | roller     | van | subway        | motorbike       |
| Color      | blood-red | emerald  | red | turquise |

