.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, lacrosse, badminton, tennis
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, skateboard, subway, quad-bike
 1. the person driving the quad-bike is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
 2. the person who's sport is tennis is not to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##8
 3. the person who's sport is cricket is the person driving the subway##1
 4. the person driving the subway is not to the right of the person driving the skateboard##8
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 6. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5
 7. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who's sport is cricket is not to the right of the person driving the subway##8
 9. the person driving the skateboard is not to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##8
10. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the left of the person driving the bike##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Sport          | lacrosse    | badminton | cricket | tennis |
| Transport   | bike | quad-bike  | subway     | skateboard    |

