2. the fan of country is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##8
3. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's birthday is in august##7
4. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5
5. the fan of ambient is somewhere to the left of the fan of electronic##5
6. the fan of trance is not to the right of the fan of ambient##8
7. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the left of the fan of electronic##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Birthday         | april  | august | march  | february  |
| Music-Genre   | trance | ambient   | electronic | country |

