.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: reading, rock-climbing, sudoku, writing
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, cain, old-henry, bongani
1. the cain-smoker is not the person who's hobby is reading##6
2. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is not to the left of the bongani-smoker##8
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the bolivar-smoker##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere between the cain-smoker and the bolivar-smoker##7
6. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
7. the old-henry-smoker is between the bongani-smoker and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing    | writing | reading | sudoku |
| Cigar   | cain | bongani      | old-henry     | bolivar     |

 